# On-device PP-OCRv5 model assets. These are large binaries fetched by
# `pnpm ocr:models` (scripts/fetch-ocr-models.mjs) and are NOT committed to git
# — same policy as the other maintainer-curated build inputs. The app serves
# whatever is present here same-origin under /models/ocr/, so nothing is loaded
# from a CDN at runtime (CLAUDE.md privacy constraint; docs/design.md §1.3, §8).
*.onnx
*.txt
!.gitignore
!README.md
